review_data: Reviewed in the United States on June 26, 2021
name: Riderz644
title: Terrific flavor
review: So delicious yogurt has a great texture and flavor. The key lime yogurt truly reminds you of key lime pie. It's also great for those who cannot have real key lime pie due to the ingredients. It's a wonderful change from the standard flavors you tend to see on the shelf in non-dairy yogurts.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on May 18, 2021
name: Starla Dear
title: Sadly a non dairy failure
review: This sadly just didn't taste good. I thought the lime and coconut flavor would match well, but I could barely bring myself to eat it. Very sad, because key lime chobani was my favorite flavor back in the days of dairy yogurt. The texture of this coconut yogurt is okay, but it's not worth the calories, especially with how low on protein it is. It's basically sugar and fat and funky lime tang.
